UInt32 Vps_IrqParams::vipIrqNum[VPS_VIP_IRQ_MAX]

Array of VIP interrupt number for each of the VIP instance. Array is defined for max VIP instances across all platforms. But only the number elements equal to VIPs available for any platform are valid.
